  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they sent us out to another work detail, which was called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That means it was a construction of a, of a hole that was constructed, a factory that was constructed for [INAUDIBLE], the big concern of [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were building this factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they put us out on this work detail.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Incidentally, every day when we marched out to work, we had to march out in the rows of fives.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by the gate as we marched out and the, and the work detail was counted in groups, every work detail, there was a band playing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had musicians outside, the finest musicians in the world.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "These were all prisoners from all over occupied Europe that they bought into Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And these musicians played violins, and flutes, clarinets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they played every morning as we marched out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And every evening when the work detail came back half dead from work, they were playing march music.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
